      "description": "Initial release — view your project vault in 3D using Filamental.\n\n## What this plugin does\n\n- Ribbon button and command to open your Obsidian vault in Filamental\n- Sidebar panel shows each note's entity type, connection count, and linked notes\n- Status bar displays entity type and connection count for Filamental nodes\n- Notes stay in sync automatically — both apps read and write the same markdown files\n\n## Requirements\n\nFilamental desktop app — free forever for one project vault, Pro for professional and commercial use. filamental.space",
